node.text: Nancy is trying to give a show of force on the house floor by forcing everyone to continue to wear a mask. ONLY on the floor though, as soon as she leaves the chamber she takes the mask off. It’s hypocrisy, it’s not surprising, and it’s a power-trip. I won’t do it. Fine me, attack me in the press, threaten me, I don’t care. The people have my back and I answer to them alone.

PSA to Joe Biden and whoever is actually running the White House, you can never give the ‘woke left’ enough. They will always be outraged, they will always be pessimistic, they will always be miserable. Stop catering to them. Serve our people, secure our nation.

node.text: I’m so moved by the fact that it was such a small number of American Patriots that stood and fought against the English Empire. It reminds me that a dedicated group of people, no matter how large, can change the world forever. Do not give up hope, although our country is in a dismal state, I believe a new American Renaissance is about to begin.
